# Temp planning files
TEMP_*.md

# data/exports/       ← NOT ignored: results.html + results.csv committed each run
# data/processed/transit_cache.json ← NOT ignored: committed to preserve transit data
# data/state/         ← NOT ignored: last_seen.json persists new-listing detection state
